text.section: In this part the following words have the meanings indicated.
"Child care center" has the meaning stated in § 5-570 of this subtitle.
"Child care provider" means a family child care provider or a child care center.
"Direct incentive grant" means a grant awarded under the Child Care Quality Incentive Grant Program.
"Family child care provider" has the meaning stated in § 5-550(d) of this subtitle.
